Yes, thank you
Good morning.

112
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:01,000
Good morning.

113
00:10:01,100 --> 00:10:02,800
Good morning, Mr. Secretary.

114
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,500
What have we got here?
A crisis in every capital?

115
00:10:05,600 --> 00:10:07,400
Uh, just one.

