117
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:11,800
Not quite.

118
00:10:13,500 --> 00:10:14,700
Here's the rest of it.

119
00:10:21,900 --> 00:10:24,600
The situation in Viet Nam
is continuing to deteriorate,

120
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:26,400
we've been able
to keep the noise level down

121
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,800
since your campaign but

122
00:10:27,900 --> 00:10:30,400
my guess is you'll be faced
with a tough decision soon.

123
