00:44:43,500 --> 00:44:45,900
so Operation Rolling Thunder
can roll on.

800
00:44:46,500 --> 00:44:47,500
Speaking with reporters,

801
00:44:47,700 --> 00:44:49,200
President Johnson emphasized

802
00:44:49,300 --> 00:44:50,900
that these thirty-five hundred
marines

803
00:44:51,100 --> 00:44:53,200
will free up
the South Vietnamese troops

804
00:44:53,300 --> 00:44:56,800
