the Vietcong inflicted
major casualties

809
00:45:07,600 --> 00:45:09,500
in Quai Nang Province.

810
00:45:09,700 --> 00:45:12,000
Unofficial sources say
that many South Vietnamese army

811
00:45:12,100 --> 00:45:13,800
units are near collapse.

812
00:45:14,700 --> 00:45:16,300
Oh, my, oh, my.

813
00:45:20,000 --> 00:45:21,000
Mr. President.

814
00:45:21,200 --> 00:45:21,800
Mr. President.

815
00:45:22,000 --> 00:45:23,700
All right, sit down, sit down boys.

816
00:45:25,100 --> 00:45:27,100
I, I heard you fellahs
were talkin over dinner.

