00:50:38,300 --> 00:50:39,500
With the seventy-one battalions,

922
00:50:39,700 --> 00:50:41,800
with Westy's plan,
this war is winnable.

923
00:50:42,000 --> 00:50:43,700
I say we go in
and we get the job done.

